CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 18, 1960, pg. B7 reads: "12. Frank Ressler, representing the McKean Oldsmobile Company, gives an enthusiastic youngster a "dry run" in a 1960 hardtop.
TitMainTitle: Frank Ressler standing next to Oldsmobile with three boys, in McKean Oldsmobile booth, at the 1960 Courier-WAMO Home-A-Rama in the Syria Mosque
